{"tid":1836304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯私人檢控西灣河開槍警員企圖謀殺　警告律政司不要介入或阻撓","createTime":"2020-01-23T07:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T02:22:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":101,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"72fbedb560e97e39e3d2677cc37d1b4df9742ae2","tid":1836304,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"去年11 月 11 日早上有示威者於西灣河一帶堵路，期間發生警民衝突，隸屬交通部警署警長關家榮於太安街及筲箕灣道交界的馬路，連開三槍實彈，其中一槍打中 21 歲香港專業教育學院學生周柏均腹部。民主黨立法會議員許智峯今日入稟法庭正式提出私人檢控，控告開槍警員企圖謀殺罪，並以意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而射擊作交替控罪，為首宗私人刑事檢控警察的案件。許於庭外表示與律師商討後認為有足夠證據提出檢控，他又警告律政司不要介入或阻撓案件，從而進一步破壞公眾對法治的信任。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯又強調自己並非針對整個警隊，而是希望個別犯錯的警察可以承擔應有的後果，正如警務處處長鄧炳強亦承認警方亦有做錯的時候，「但係偏偏我哋睇唔到個別警員受到任何懲罰或者法律制裁」。許又透露現階段暫未有支付任何律師費用，及為打官司而發起的眾籌至今已籌得338萬元。另外，許智峯一方曾就擔任證人事宜與中槍事主的律師代表有所接觸，他明白對方就出任證人牽涉「複雜法律考慮」，例如會否被起訴等，故許希望最理想的情況是不用傳召對方作供，亦有足夠證據定罪。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯法律團隊律師楊浩然表則指，是市民以私人檢控控告警暴屬史無前例，他們於檢控方面對不少困惱，包括資源不足、缺乏蒐證權利，及要面對警方龐大的法律團隊及律政司隨時介入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E6%88%96%E9%98%BB%E6%92%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2592%2593%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=87b6ce68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2592%2593%2F&h=2344fbfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E6%88%96%E9%98%BB%E6%92%93/</a>"},{"pid":"c9083bce5f99444eeba0c8367008e9fbc17f2eed","tid":1836304,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54b5649773a4aa5beaf1f506fec55081a5a72d8d","tid":1836304,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da383a3d1071b464039fd2cc07ed4aab7e9e855","tid":1836304,"uid":14678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484ae1d0f62a038acebc23d0cb3ed483458dd880","tid":1836304,"uid":271516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"許智勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76649df2ab69034fb227f9535a095a778fd6c627","tid":1836304,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db038e997af2c87cbfbb08b5